title: Nuclear Fusion Breakthrough Gets a Bigger Burst of Laser Energy
description: Researchers at the National Ignition Facility during a July firing of 192 lasers improved on a December result, but also ended up with duds in other experiments.

title: Amazon to Invest Up to $4 Billion in A.I. Start-Up Anthropic
description: With its investment of up to $4 billion, Amazon is seeking a bigger footprint in A.I. development, one already established by rivals like Microsoft and Google.

title: Amazon to Invest Up to $4 Billion in A.I. Start-up Anthropic
description: Tech giants have been partnering with up-and-coming A.I. start-ups, like Microsoft backing OpenAI, but Amazon has not been as active as rivals until now.

title: The Secret Ingredient of ChatGPT Is Human Advice
description: Companies like OpenAI hone their bots using hand-tailored examples from well-educated workers. But is this always for the best?

title: Air Force Receives Its First Electric Air Taxi
description: Joby Aviation delivered the aircraft, which can carry a pilot and four passengers, to Edwards Air Force Base in California for testing.

title: ChatGPT Can Now Respond With Spoken Words
description: A new version of OpenAI’s popular chatbot behaves a lot like Siri and Alexa. You can talk to it — and have a conversation.

title: Egg Crack Challenge and Cheese Slice Trick: Are Parents OK?
description: With the “cheese slice trick” and the “egg crack challenge,” parents vie for viral recognition — and the illusion of control over their children.
